{"tid":2452633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Chemsex 用藥性愛知多啲 Know More and No More","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T05:53:12.000Z","uid":311499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aad6a37646be2d624590c98ac066693a5f22eabb","tid":2452633,"uid":311499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"Chemsex用藥性愛是指在性行為時濫用娛樂性藥物（即毒品）來提升性興奮程度，近年在本地男男族群內尤其盛行。2017年衞生防護中心發表的「香港男男性接觸者愛滋病風險及流行情況調查」(PRiSM)中發現，近17%受訪者曾在性行為期間使用毒品，令進行高危無套性行為的比率持續上升，情況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓大家全面理解Chemsex，基金會邀請香港大學社會學系劉凱亮博士主持網上工作坊第一集，深入淺出剖析「誰會玩」、「邊度玩」、「玩邊啲」、「點解玩」及「點危險」。工作坊詳情如下︰<br />\n<br />\nKnow More Chemsex | Chemsex No More 1.0 <br />\n日期︰3月26日（星期五）<br />\n時間︰晚上8:30<br />\n形式︰基金會Facebook LIVE直播<br />\n*預告︰Know More Chemsex | Chemsex No More 2.0 將會更深入講解Chemsex用藥性愛的迷思、經歷、傷害、急救、出路<br />\n<br />\n免責聲明: 此活動旨在讓公眾全面理解「用藥性愛Chemfun / Chemsex行為」對使用者的危害與涉及的風險。嘉賓言論純屬個人意見，不代表基金會立場。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tExWcm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tExWcm.jpg&h=b39aff52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c9f50288edb4633d7575c2ddac179725149e8fd","tid":2452633,"uid":311499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"自推一次先<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/38R03bN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38R03bN&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=b264132b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38R03bN</a>"},{"pid":"1728f94d3f4f11a43b361fde0fed264586d91fe6","tid":2452633,"uid":23829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"抄我名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72abdb5b91435db193a839772239f9067af2b6d","tid":2452633,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1728f94d3f4f11a43b361fde0fed264586d91fe6","tid":2452633,"uid":23829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:45:51.0